triageapp.components

Class VitalSigns

  • java.lang.Object
    • triageapp.components.VitalSigns
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class VitalSigns
extends Object
implements Serializable
    VitalSigns stores the vital signs (eg. blood pressure, temperature, heart rate) of a patient at the time he/she was checked.
